HEADWORD: Patibulary
<hw>Pa*tib"u*la*ry</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>patibulum</ets> a gallows: cf. F. <ets>patibulaire</ets>.]</ety>
<def>Of or pertaining to the gallows, or to execution.</def>
